title: Proton 9.0 (Beta16) brings more regression fixes, updated Steamworks SDK
description: Valve have released another Beta version of Proton 9.0, what will become the next main stable version of Proton on the path to getting as many games running as possible on Linux Desktop / Steam Deck.

title: Windows compatibility layer Wine 9.5 released
description: Another two weeks are done and so a fresh update of the Windows compatibility layer is live with the Wine 9.5 development release.
